---
title: BBQ Chicken Pizza with Pepper, Onion and Rocket
description: Making your own pizza from scratch is one of the best cooking experiences and will leave your kitchen smelling amazing. This particular recipe is a recreation of a pizza Chef Lizzie enjoyed on a recent holiday to Italy and is guaranteed to become an instant weeknight hit. For an authentic Italian taste, our pizza has a thin and crispy base, topped with peppers, sweet BBQ chicken and creamy mozzarella. Serve in the centre of your table, top with peppery rocket and grab a slice before it’s gone!
